    <title>Hexo 博客主题 Lx</title>
    <url>/190607/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/blleng/images@master/upload/lx-test.jpeg" alt="View"></p>
<p><code>Lx</code>是一款简洁、美观的Hexo主题。</p>
<p>Languages: <a href="/200318/">English</a>, 中文<br>当前版本：<code>dev</code><br>项目地址：<a href="https://github.com/blleng/hexo-theme-lx">https://github.com/blleng/hexo-theme-lx</a></p>
<span id="more"></span>

<div class="note success">
            <p>项目地址：<a href="https://github.com/blleng/hexo-theme-lx">https://github.com/blleng/hexo-theme-lx</a></p><p>作者的博客：<a href="https://freezing.cool/">https://freezing.cool</a></p><p>需要帮助、报告bug或提出建议请提交issue：<br><a href="https://github.com/blleng/hexo-theme-lx/issues">https://github.com/blleng/hexo-theme-lx/issues</a></p>
          </div>

<div class="note warning">
            <p>本站为<code>lx</code>主题提供<code>dev</code>分支的测试，而非为大家提供帮助，如若需要帮助、报告bug或提出建议请务必提交issue。</p>
          </div>

<h2 id="使用"><a href="#使用" class="headerlink" title="使用"></a>使用</h2><h3 id="克隆到本地："><a href="#克隆到本地：" class="headerlink" title="克隆到本地："></a>克隆到本地：</h3><p>在博客根目录:</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/blleng/hexo-theme-lx themes/lx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="启用本主题："><a href="#启用本主题：" class="headerlink" title="启用本主题："></a>启用本主题：</h3><p>更改站点设置文件<code>_config.yml</code>:</p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">theme:</span> <span class="string">lx</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>主题的配置将在<code>themes/lx/_config.yml</code>中进行。</p>
<h2 id="配置"><a href="#配置" class="headerlink" title="配置"></a>配置</h2><p>详情参见<code>README</code>文档：</p>
<a class="btn" href="https://github.com/blleng/hexo-theme-lx" title="README"><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right fa-fw"></i>Hexo-Theme-Lx</a>

<h2 id="已完成"><a href="#已完成" class="headerlink" title="已完成"></a>已完成</h2><ul>
<li>Comment 评论</li>
<li>Analytics 统计<ul>
<li>Baidu Analytics （百度）</li>
<li>Goole Analytics （谷歌）</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Mathjax 数学公式（支持化学方程式）</li>
<li>Font-Awesome</li>
<li>Next主题的部分标签<ul>
<li>label</li>
<li>button</li>
<li>note</li>
<li>video</li>
<li>etc…</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>SideBar 侧边栏</li>
<li>Social 社交媒体链接</li>
<li>LocalSearch 本地搜索</li>
<li>tags 文章标签页面</li>
<li>category 文章分类页面</li>
<li>jsdelivr静态资源加速</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="待完成"><a href="#待完成" class="headerlink" title="待完成"></a>待完成</h2><ul>
<li>PJAX支持</li>
<li>Fancybox支持</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="特性展示"><a href="#特性展示" class="headerlink" title="特性展示"></a>特性展示</h2><h3 id="Mathjax"><a href="#Mathjax" class="headerlink" title="Mathjax"></a>Mathjax</h3><p>数学公式：</p>
<p>万有引力常数为 \(G\)，对于质量分别为 \(M\) 和 \(m\)，球心距离为 \(r\) 的两个正球形天体，两者间相互作用力：</p>
<p>$$F=\frac{GMm}{r^2}$$</p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">万有引力常数为\\(G\\),对于质量分别为\\(M\\)和\\(m\\)，球心距离为\\(r\\)的两个正球形天体，两者间相互作用力：</span><br><span class="line">$$F=\frac&#123;GMm&#125;&#123;r^2&#125;$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>化学方程式：</p>
<p>$$\ce{CH2=CH2 + Cl2 -&gt; CH2Cl-CH2Cl}$$</p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$\ce&#123;CH2=CH2 + Cl2 -&gt; CH2Cl-CH2Cl&#125;$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="代码块"><a href="#代码块" class="headerlink" title="代码块"></a>代码块</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><figcaption><span>Hello World!</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span><span class="string">&lt;cstdio&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> namespae std;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;hello world!&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="Note-tag"><a href="#Note-tag" class="headerlink" title="Note tag"></a>Note tag</h3><div class="note default">
            <h4 id="note-default"><a href="#note-default" class="headerlink" title="note default"></a>note default</h4><p>default</p>
          </div>

<div class="note info">
            <h4 id="note-info"><a href="#note-info" class="headerlink" title="note info"></a>note info</h4><p>info</p>
          </div>

<div class="note primary">
            <h4 id="note-primary"><a href="#note-primary" class="headerlink" title="note primary"></a>note primary</h4><p>primary</p>
          </div>

<div class="note success">
            <h4 id="note-success"><a href="#note-success" class="headerlink" title="note success"></a>note success</h4><p>success</p>
          </div>

<div class="note warning">
            <h4 id="note-warning"><a href="#note-warning" class="headerlink" title="note warning"></a>note warning</h4><p>warning</p>
          </div>

<div class="note danger">
            <h4 id="note-danger"><a href="#note-danger" class="headerlink" title="note danger"></a>note danger</h4><p>danger</p>
          </div>

<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note default%&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">### note default</span></span><br><span class="line">default</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="Label-tag"><a href="#Label-tag" class="headerlink" title="Label tag"></a>Label tag</h3><span class="label default">复道</span><span class="label primary">行空</span>，<span class="label default">不霁</span><span class="label success">何虹</span>。<span class="label info">长桥</span><span class="label danger">卧波</span>，<span class="label warning">未云</span><mark>何龙</mark>。

<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;%label @复道%&#125;&#123;%label primary@行空%&#125;，&#123;%label default@不霁%&#125;&#123;%label success@何虹%&#125;。</span><br><span class="line">&#123;%label info@长桥%&#125;&#123;%label danger@卧波%&#125;，&#123;%label warning@未云%&#125;<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">mark</span>&gt;</span></span>何龙<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">mark</span>&gt;</span></span>。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="Button-tag"><a href="#Button-tag" class="headerlink" title="Button tag"></a>Button tag</h3><p>Basic button</p>
<a class="btn" href="#url" title="title">test_tile</a>

<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;%btn #url,test<span class="emphasis">_tile,,title%&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>With icon</p>
<a class="btn" href="#url"><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i>test_tile</a>

<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;%btn #url,test<span class="emphasis">_tile,hand-o-right%&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>Fix-width</p>
<a class="btn" href="#url"><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right fa-fw"></i>test_tile</a>

<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;%btn #url,test<span class="emphasis">_tile,hand-o-right fa-fw %&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="Center-quote-tag"><a href="#Center-quote-tag" class="headerlink" title="Center-quote tag"></a>Center-quote tag</h3><blockquote class='blockquote-center'><p>人类的悲欢并不相通，我只觉得他们吵闹。</br><strong>——鲁迅</strong></p>
</blockquote>

<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;%cq%&#125; something &#123;%endcq%&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="Video-tag"><a href="#Video-tag" class="headerlink" title="Video tag"></a>Video tag</h3><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% video url %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
